# Mental Health Wellness Platform üå±

A comprehensive mental health application focusing on journaling, meditation, and community support. Built with the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js) and Tailwind CSS.

## Key Features ‚ú®
- **User Authentication**: JWT-based secure login/registration
- **Personalized Dashboard**: Mood tracking, activity stats, and daily affirmations
- **Journaling System**: 
  - Streak tracking with progress visualization
  - Rich text entries with prompts
  - Entry history with search/filter
- **Meditation Hub**: Guided sessions for different needs (mindfulness, anxiety relief)
- **Secure Chat**: Real-time communication with mental health professionals
- **Responsive UI**: Mobile-first design with calming color schemes

